  "id": "RAW_7e8fc08c",
  "title": "介绍 TRIBE v2：一款旨在理解人脑如何处理复杂刺激的预测性基础模型",
  "url": "https://ai.meta.com/blog/tribe-v2-brain-predictive-foundation-model/",
  "date": "2026-03-25 16:00:00",
  "author": "AI at Meta Blog",
  "siteName": "AI at Meta Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"_li\">\n   <div class=\"_8xs5\">\n    <div class=\"_9rdv _9bie _9bif _9bhn _9kum _9o9f\">\n     <div class=\"_aqmz _aqp3\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n      <div>\n       <div class=\"_aqmc _aqmd\">\n        <div class=\"_9bhp _9bhq _9bg- _9bh0 _9bh9 _9bhv _9998 _ar3s _as9p _9mp7 _8h4k\" style=\"padding:0px 24px;display:flex;font-size:12px;flex-flow:column wrap;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;max-width:750px;width:750px;justify-content:center;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;align-items:flex-start;\">\n         <p class=\"_a92o _a5e5 _a5w7\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.01em;font-size:36px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Optimistic Display Medium&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:43.2px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;margin-bottom:0px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\">Takeaways</p>\n         <div class=\"_a5gf _a5gi _a5i4 _a5ji\" style=\"padding-top:24px;width:702px;\"></div>\n         <div class=\"_a5ci _a5cs _a92o _a5c- _a5w7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Optimistic Text Normal&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px;\">\n          <ul class=\"_90f8\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">\n           <li style=\"margin-left:2em;\">We're introducing TRIBE v2<span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-family: &quot;Optimistic Text Bold&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">,</span>&nbsp;our next-gen model that acts as a digital twin of human neural activity. This offers unprecedented speed, accuracy, and a 70x resolution increase as compared to similar models to predict how the brain responds to almost any sight or sound — enabling neuroscientists and clinical researchers to test theories without requiring human subjects.</li>\n           <li style=\"margin-left:2em;\">We're releasing the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/facebook/tribev2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 224);\"><u>model</u></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/facebookresearch/tribev2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 224);\"><u>codebase</u></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ai.meta.com/research/publications/a-foundation-model-of-vision-audition-and-language-for-in-silico-neuroscience/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 224);\"><u>paper</u></a>, and an&nbsp;<a href=\"http://aidemos.atmeta.com/tribev2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 224);\"><u>interactive demo</u></a>&nbsp;to help researchers push the boundaries of neuroscience, apply brain insights to build better AI systems, and use computational simulation to accelerate breakthroughs in the treatment of neurological disorders.</li>\n          </ul>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"_a5gf _a5gi _a5i4 _a5ji\" style=\"padding-top:24px;width:702px;\"></div>\n         <p class=\"_a92o _a5c- _a5w7\" style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Optimistic Text Normal&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;margin-bottom:0px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\">Understanding how the human brain processes the world around us is one of the greatest open challenges in neuroscience. Breakthroughs here could transform how we understand and treat neurological conditions affecting hundreds of millions of people — and improve AI systems by directly guiding their development from neuroscientific principles.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"_9bhp _9bhq _9bhs _9bh0 _9bh9 _9bhv _9998 _ar3s _as9p _9mp7 _8h4l\" style=\"padding:0px 24px;display:flex;font-size:12px;flex-flow:column wrap;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;max-width:950px;width:100%;justify-content:center;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;align-items:center;\">\n         <div class=\"_a5gf _a5gi _a5i4 _a5ji\" style=\"padding-top:24px;width:100%;\"></div>\n         <div data-testid=\"responsive-video\" id=\"u_0_6_x6\">\n          <span id=\"u_0_7_Ek\"></span>\n          <video src=\"https://video-sea1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m366/AQMP-6thYLChd6kZm7LUN6L_cZOzouzdKRCcElR-MCFFYPJq92fOqwj-XpYWEx09dSrSV6P-hH88xrNgwhfrCo_0vY8DIbtWkL6E0EsO2Wq05A.mp4?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=video-sea1-1.xx.fbcdn.net&amp;_nc_ohc=K4UM8fn6CiMQ7kNvwHcP1Hf&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5GQUNFQk9PSy4uQzMuMTI4MC5kYXNoX2gyNjQtYmFzaWMtZ2VuMl83MjBwIiwieHB2X2Fzc2V0X2lkIjoxNjMyMTAxOTExNDQ0NjMyLCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6MCwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAxMjgsImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjI5LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=6e378936983291d9&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=vj0cwHU08qbMi4JuIdndNg&amp;_nc_ss=7a30f&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;oh=00_Afx8eV1TieG3rogGVsBQhTprXmutxZR0euFYEaaC0CFD3Q&amp;oe=69CB26A8&amp;bitrate=461403&amp;tag=dash_h264-basic-gen2_720p\" class=\"_9rzn _9lwe\" controls=\"1\" controlslist=\"nodownload\" loop=\"1\" muted=\"1\" playsinline=\"1\" poster=\"https://scontent-sea5-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.8562-6/656903822_1924587398162998_8188706083301003117_n.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=f537c7&amp;_nc_ohc=fJtXDqJ4CeAQ7kNvwFA19Vh&amp;_nc_oc=AdovqkpDsct7em9-Yno56R3SUDRTJi5ZhCAeRBM1igZ2VQZOLAY7yV9mope56CUx06c&amp;_nc_zt=14&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sea5-1.xx&amp;_nc_gid=vj0cwHU08qbMi4JuIdndNg&amp;_nc_ss=7a30f&amp;oh=00_Afy3m4yHf7pC2_ry6vxTtZUt6oG-brGeqeJn-Jvuz6LC0w&amp;oe=69CB1A57\" id=\"u_0_8_W+\" style=\"width:100%;\"></video>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"_a5gf _a5gi _a5i4 _a5ji\" style=\"padding-top:24px;width:100%;\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"_9bhp _9bhq _9bg- _9bh0 _9bh9 _9bhv _9998 _ar3s _as9p _9mp7 _8h4k\" style=\"padding:0px 24px;display:flex;font-size:12px;flex-flow:column wrap;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;max-width:750px;width:750px;justify-content:center;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;align-items:flex-start;\">\n         <div class=\"_a5ci _a5cs _a92o _a5c- _a5w7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Optimistic Text Normal&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">Today, we're announcing TRIBE v2: our first AI model of human brain responses to sights, sounds, and language. Building on our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2508.10784v1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 224);\"><u>Algonauts 2025 award-winning model</u></a>, which was trained on the low-resolution fMRI recordings of four individuals, we leverage a massive dataset of more than 700 healthy volunteers who were presented with a wide variety of media, including images, podcasts, videos, and text. TRIBE v2 reliably predicts high-resolution fMRI brain activity — enabling zero-shot predictions for new subjects, languages, and tasks, and consistently outperforms standard modeling approaches. By creating a digital model of the human brain, researchers can rapidly test hypotheses about its underlying functions without the need for human subjects in every experiment.</p>\n          <p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">To accelerate the pace of neuroscience discovery and open up new avenues for clinical practice, we’re sharing a research paper, along with model weights and code, under a CC BY-NC license. We also invite everyone to explore TRIBE v2 on our demo website. By sharing this work, we hope to help accelerate neuroscience research that will unlock scientific and clinical breakthroughs for the greater good.</p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div></div>\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yF/r/vrFP_lijce7.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yr/l/0,cross/8vzypSmV3M0.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yM/r/du-lggJFMTd.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yq/r/3LUm4qqziVl.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yD/l/0,cross/MnA5-2-8ab9.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/y2/l/0,cross/iffhxWiN5x0.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/ym/l/0,cross/iLurgXoICDY.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yz/l/0,cross/b8bT8K6wJb8.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yw/l/0,cross/NdI56imvkTb.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yq/r/zJ1_a2c4j_s.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/y3/r/G9ppKZS4BSb.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yI/r/UNViX7Cuc1c.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4iuEM4/yQ/l/en_US-j/qwz40QHjjrw.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/y7/r/fQ-a5Ttu39i.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yb/l/0,cross/iVelFfnZnjr.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yZ/r/lq8mONCkWDG.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4in2s4/y3/l/en_US-j/nxBCco19BlS.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yp/r/Yaytv1eYkHw.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yd/r/Zmk7k67QPCp.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yP/r/7I0bX2I9jaF.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yA/l/0,cross/67AV6U2wn1E.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yO/r/-33UUS3AzeU.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4iK_F4/yp/l/en_US-j/pDZ__Jx0WsM.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/y4/r/_ik5qo1rIEU.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/ym/r/EdiJ8stEpPk.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4i2TV4/yZ/l/en_US-j/vxxiPMpi6Ta.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4i7M54/yI/l/en_US-j/TaaBUNsHLTc.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/yU/r/KSwKqkTiCZ0.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v4/ye/r/plXIyg5ns3p.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" nonce=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yN/l/0,cross/hivjlTCw0qp.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yd/l/0,cross/TwC-oH0eOdE.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yb/l/0,cross/_sDsWIjRQq_.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/ys/l/0,cross/Tb4rtCLBRvY.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yB/l/0,cross/e0NPbEB7XGP.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/y9/l/0,cross/Z0lHNn7GS5u.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v5/yT/l/0,cross/vksnXFsxEKe.css\" as=\"style\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Meta 推出了 TRIBE v2，这是一款高分辨率预测性基础模型，可作为人类神经活动的数字孪生，用于模拟大脑对视觉、听觉和语言刺激的反应。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Meta 推出了 TRIBE v2，这是一款高分辨率预测性基础模型，可作为人类神经活动的数字孪生，用于模拟大脑对视觉、听觉和语言刺激的反应。",
  "summary": "Meta 发布了 TRIBE v2，这是一款旨在预测人脑对复杂刺激反应的下一代基础模型。基于先前的研究，TRIBE v2 在超过 700 名志愿者的海量数据集上进行了训练，在预测 fMRI 大脑反应方面，其分辨率比早期模型提高了 70 倍。它支持针对新受试者、语言和任务的零样本（zero-shot）预测，有效地充当了计算机模拟神经科学（in silico neuroscience）的数字孪生。通过开源模型权重、代码库和研究论文，Meta 旨在加速神经系统疾病治疗的突破，并为类脑 AI 架构的开发提供参考。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "TRIBE v2 可作为人类神经活动的高分辨率数字孪生。",
      "explanation": "该模型预测大脑对视觉、听觉和语言反应的分辨率比之前版本高出 70 倍，使研究人员无需人类受试者即可验证假设。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型展现了强大的零样本泛化能力。",
      "explanation": "TRIBE v2 在超过 700 名志愿者的数据上进行训练，能够可靠地预测新个体以及训练过程中未曾遇到的多样化任务的大脑活动。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Meta 已将该研究完全开源，以促进科学合作。",
      "explanation": "通过在 CC BY-NC 许可下发布模型权重、代码和论文，Meta 为社区提供了加速临床研究和 AI 开发的工具。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "TRIBE v2：我们首个模拟人脑对视觉、听觉和语言反应的 AI 模型。",
    "与同类模型相比，它提供了前所未有的速度、准确性，并将预测大脑对几乎任何视觉或听觉刺激反应的分辨率提高了 70 倍。",
    "通过创建人脑的数字模型，研究人员可以快速验证关于其潜在功能假设，而无需在每次实验中都依赖人类受试者。"
  ],
